archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.name: Security Framework Motivation
archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation:
This view shows stakeholders and drivers which can be associated to motivate Security Framework implementation within Tietoevry Tech Services
View is built to show how generic high level drivers are connected on utilizing existing industrial standard Architecture AND Security Arhictecture Frameworks.
It also shows how SABSA and TOGAF Frameworks could provide the common framework
